(A: Hwang Gi Chan, B: Hwang Ji Ho)

00:31:47.231 --> 00:31:51.041
(Are not biologically related)

00:32:33.051 --> 00:32:36.751
(Queen's House)

00:32:37.381 --> 00:32:39.091
To really set them up,

00:32:39.251 --> 00:32:41.791
I need to get them alone together one more time.

00:32:41.861 --> 00:32:42.861
Stop...

00:32:43.421 --> 00:32:44.691
with the Cupid act.

00:32:45.831 --> 00:32:47.391
It's because I like Jae In.

00:32:49.561 --> 00:32:53.101
Darkness is the side of time that makes us remember the light.

00:32:56.001 --> 00:32:57.741
This looks like Kim Do Hee's handwriting.

00:32:58.041 --> 00:33:00.511
You didn't know you were being fooled?

00:33:00.711 --> 00:33:03.781
Kang Jae In. Don't trust me too much.

00:33:04.811 --> 00:33:06.651
I knew it. You really are a piece of trash.

00:33:06.881 --> 00:33:10.420
I'll be throwing you in the trash, so just wait.

00:33:10.421 --> 00:33:11.551
Bingo.